CatDescriptText: Descriptions of doll scenes reads "Friendly Fran makes friends around the world when she is recognized in a G.R. Club"  "Gay Gertie goes in for sports plays a mean game of tennis in her cute little shorts"  "Jitterbug Josie and the B.F. swing out at a G.R. Party"
TitMainTitle: Two women standing on either side of table with dolls posed in scenes with descriptions, and sign above display inscribed "Induct Yourself Good Times Girl Reserves"
